name: source
description: Name of the source node for that section of the Sankey diagram flow. Using the final names I would like on the plot, because the networkD3 package to generate the Sankey plot will not allow me to edit the label names later.

name: target
description: Name of the target node for that section of the Sankey diagram flow. Using the final names I would like on the plot, because the networkD3 package to generate the Sankey plot will not allow me to edit the label names later.

name: value
description: Number of worms, indicating how wide that part of the Sankey diagram flow should be.
